		<th class="thHead" align="left">New direction!  New theme!</th>
	</tr>

	<tr>
		<td class="row1"><span class="postbody">I've been doing some extensive reading on the <a href="http://www.piratesoftheburningsea.com" target="_blank" class="postlink">Pirates of the Burning Sea website</a> and I'm convinced this is going to be great game.  In many ways it is similar to Shadowbane and I'm really looking forward to seeing it released.  Unfortunately it hasn't even entered beta-test yet :/  Though they claim it will be released this winter.  I know it's a long time to wait, but I think it will be worth it.  The fantasy genre has a lot of people bored, myself including.  I expect this will be a refreshing change and will bring a lot of players aboard (so to speak).
<br />

<br />
I'll be in the process of updating the theme for the page in anticipation of PBS, Nanook if you're out there, your help would be most appreciated.  Would also be good to hear from you dude. ...<br /><a href=".//forum/viewtopic.php?t=1009&amp;sid=3d1f123f0f0860a8b16419d8dc75fce9"><span class="gensmall">Read more</span></a>&nbsp;</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
	</tr>
