		<th class="thHead" align="left">Emergency Hotfix</th>
	</tr>

	<tr>
		<td class="row1"><span class="postbody">As discussed on Friday, we updated the Test Server with a patch that will fix the various ways that some players are using game exploits.  We will be taking down the production game servers soon to apply this patch to them.  Once updated, we will evaluate the effect it has and make any adjustments that need to be made.  Furthermore, we are scheduling an extended server downtime tomorrow for further action should this not rectify the performance issues that are currently being experienced.  Do realize that this is the Shadowbane Team's highest priority and that all of our assets are working towards this before we continue work on A Call to Arms.  Once we do have this issue behind us, though, we will move ahead on completing the update that we originally had scheduled to go to the Test server tomorrow.
<br />

<br />
